## üíæ Installation

### üì¶ PyPI

```bash
pip install torchsom
```

### üîß Development Version

```bash
git clone https://github.com/michelin/TorchSOM.git
cd TorchSOM
python3.9 -m venv .torchsom_env
source .torchsom_env/bin/activate
pip install -e ".[all]"
```

